        <updateDate>2012-04-27T20:11:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Veterans Work Study Opportunities Act - Makes permanent the authority of the Secretary of Veterans Affairs to provide a work-study allowance for certain activities of individuals receiving educational assistance through the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA). (Under current law, such authority extends only through the period preceding June 30, 2013.)</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
